<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Echitatie in desert si pe plaja</title>
    <style>
        .back{
            font-size: 27px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: black;
        }
        .paragraph{
            font-size: 25px;
        }
        .back:hover{
            color: rgb(37, 37, 37);
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .paragraph{
                font-size: 25px;
                width: 280vw;
            }
        }
        .translation-btn-usa{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1300px;
        }
        .translation-btn-ro{
            position: absolute;
            height: 50px;
            width: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: -80px;
            margin-left: 1390px;
        }
        .invisible{
            display: none;
            top: -1000000px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a class="back" href="/hurghada/home">     <p class="back">←</p>    </a>
    <div class="translation">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_the_United_States.svg.png" class="translation-btn-usa" id="translation-btn-usa">
        <img src="/images/1200px-Flag_of_Romania.svg.png" class="translation-btn-ro" id="translation-btn-ro">
    </div>
    <h1>Echitatie in desert si pe plaja</h1>
    <p id="paragraph-ro" class="paragraph">
        Veti incepe ziua admirand frumusetea muntilor din desert. Veti fi preluati de la hotel in jurul orei 15, si veti merge sa descoperiti in desert satul beduinilor.
        Transportul va fi asigurat de o masina de teren. Veti admira astfel de la inaltimea unei camile frumusetile naturii, muntii si apusul de soare.
        Ajunsi din nou cu picioarele pe pamant veti putea participa la spectacolul stelelor cu ajutorul unui telescop.
        Pe durata calatoriei veti fi serviti cu apa si bauturi racoritoare dupa care veti lua cina privind fabulosul cer instelat.
        Aici mica noastra excursie va lua sfarsit urmand sa va conducem la hotel in jurul orei 19:30.
        Deci v-am convins?
        Va asteptam cu drag !!!
        <br><br>
        Pret:<br>
        Adult: 35 €<br>
        Copil: 18 €<br><br>
        Cand:<br>
    </p>
    <p id="paragraph-usa" class="paragraph invisible">
        You will start the day admiring the beauty of the desert mountains. You will be picked up from the hotel around 3 pm, and you will go to discover the Bedouin village in the desert.
        Transportation will be provided by an off-road vehicle. You will admire the beauty of nature, the mountains and the sunset from the height of a camel.
        Arriving again with your feet on the ground, you will be able to participate in the spectacle of the stars with the help of a telescope.
        During the trip you will be served with water and soft drinks after which you will have dinner on the fabulous starry sky.
        Here our little trip will end and we will take you to the hotel around 19:30.
        So I convinced you?
        You're welcome !!!
        <br><br>
        Price:<br>
        Adult: 35 €<br>
        Children: 18 €
        <br><br>
        When:<br>
    </p>
</body>
<script>
    const translateBtnUsa = document.getElementById("translation-btn-usa")
    const translateBtnRo = document.getElementById("translation-btn-ro")
    const paragraphUsa = document.getElementById("paragraph-usa")
    const paragraphRo = document.getElementById("paragraph-ro")

    translateBtnUsa.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.remove("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.add("invisible")
    })

    translateBtnRo.addEventListener("click", ()=>{
        paragraphUsa.classList.add("invisible")
        paragraphRo.classList.remove("invisible")
    })

</script>
</html>